n\n<font face=\"arial, helvetica\" size=\"-1\"><b>David Berlind</b><br>\n\n\n<font size=\"+1\"><a href=\"http://techupdate.zdnet.com/techupdate/stories/main/0,14179,2874762,00.html\n\">\n<b>Hey, thief! This laptop is locked</b></a></font><br>\n\nTry stealing my notebook and <b>Caveo Anti-Theft</b> will yell at you louder and louder -- before resorting to an unstoppable, ear-piercing screech. It's motion detection on a PC Card.<br>\n\n<img src=\"http://www.zdnet.com/techupdate/i/arrow_blue.gif\" width=\"8\" height=\"10\" border=\"0\"><font size=\"-1\">\n<a href=\"http://clickthru.online.com/Click?q=08-IFoQIRjTZPn901Hg3F-erCpGY9iR\" >\n<b>And it's virtually foolproof</b></a></font><br>\n\n<img src=\"http://www.zdnet.com/techupdate/i/arrow_blue.gif\" width=\"8\" height=\"10\" border=\"0\"><font size=\"-1\">\n<a href=\"http://clickthru.online.com/Click?q=1d-6KTjIGQTqzqmQb3Rl28NRQSnqQPR\" ><b>Also: Start-up has locks for Secure Notebook</b></a></font>\n\n</font>\n\n<img src=\"http://www.zdnet.com/b.gif\" width=1 height=8><br>\n</td>\n\n<td width=5 rowspan=2><img src=\"http://www.zdnet.com/b.gif\" width=5 height=1></td>\n<td width=5 bgcolor=\"#fffff3\" rowspan=2><img src=\"http://www.zdnet.com/b.gif\" width=5 height=1></td>\n<td width=160 bgcolor=\"#fffff3\" rowspan=2><img src=\"http://www.zdnet.com/b.gif\" width=1 height=7><br>\n<font face=\"verdana, arial\" size=\"-2\">\n\n\n\n<!---- HEADLINES---->\n\n<b>Latest from ZDNet News</b><br><img src=\"http://www.zdnet.com/b.gif\" width=1 height=5><br>\n\n<img src=\"http://www.zdnet.com/b.gif\" height=7 width=1><br>\n<img src=\"http://www.zdnet.com/techupdate/i/arrow_blue.gif\" width=\"8\" height=\"10\" border=\"0\">\n<a href=\"http://clickthru.online.com/Click?q=32-Gx5IIrQi8BLS9sqDFWVhZSgRXBnR\" >Earnings: Breaking the bottom line</a><br>\n\n<img src=\"http://www.zdnet.com/b.gif\" height=7 width=1><br>\n<img src=\"http://www.zdnet.com/techupdate/i/arrow_blue.gif\" width=\"8\" height=\"10\" border=\"0\">\n<a href=\"http://click